article.description: — Cameron Henry's 22 points helped Indiana State defeat Drexel 85-81 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Henry puts up 22 in Indiana State's 85-81 win against Drexel
article.linkText: Henry puts up 22 in Indiana State's 85-81 win against Drexel
article.story: ESTERO, Fla. -- — Cameron Henry's 22 points helped Indiana State defeat Drexel 85-81 on Wednesday night. Henry added 10 rebounds and six assists for the Sycamores (5-1). Xavier Bledson scored 22 points while going 8 of 14 from the floor, including 1 for 4 from distance, and 5 for 5 from the line. Robbie Avila recorded 11 points and shot 4 for 5, including 3 for 4 from beyond the arc. Lamar Oden Jr. finished with 16 points for the Dragons (3-3). Amari Williams added 15 points and three steals for Drexel. Justin Moore also had 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
